"title": "5558: storing",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5558: storing",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A laying up of surpluses for times of scarcity. It includes such facilities as store cities and storehouses and also refers to hoarding treasures. Figuratively the word is used of the accumulation of human sin and God's consequent judgment.</p>\n<h2>Store cities</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:11\">EXO 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:35\">GEN 41:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:48\">GEN 41:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:19\">1KI 9:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:4-2Chr8:6\">2CH 8:4–8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:4\">2CH 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:12-2Chr17:13\">2CH 17:12–17:13</a></p>\n<h2>Storehouses</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:56\">GEN 41:56</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:7\">1KI 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:51\">1KI 7:51</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:1\">2CH 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:14\">2KI 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:15\">2KI 18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:13\">2KI 24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:15\">1CH 26:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:25\">1CH 27:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:15\">2CH 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:2\">2CH 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:10-2Chr31:11\">2CH 31:10–31:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27-2Chr32:28\">2CH 32:27–32:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:69\">EZR 2:69</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:9\">EST 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:4\">PRO 24:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">MAL 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41-Mark12:44\">MRK 12:41–12:44</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1-Luke21:4\">LUK 21:1–21:4</a></p>\n<h2>The contents of storehouses</h2>\n<h3>Materials kept in storage</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:21\">GEN 6:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:34-Gen41:35\">GEN 41:34–41:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:49\">GEN 41:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:51\">1KI 7:51</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:1\">2CH 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr11:11\">2CH 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:5\">2CH 31:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:11-2Chr31:12\">2CH 31:11–31:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27-2Chr32:28\">2CH 32:27–32:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:15\">EZR 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:17\">EZR 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:1-Ezra6:2\">EZR 6:1–6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:5\">EZR 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:37-Neh10:39\">NEH 10:37–10:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:28\">ISA 10:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer41:8\">JER 41:8</a></p>\n<h3>Empty storehouses a disaster</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:17\">JOL 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:35-Gen41:36\">GEN 41:35–41:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:25\">1CH 27:25</a></p>\n<h2>Roofs and watchtowers provided storage space</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:6\">JOS 2:6</a></strong></p>\n<h2>God's storehouse</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:7\">PSA 135:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:12\">DEU 28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:34\">DEU 32:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:17\">JOB 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:22-Job38:23\">JOB 38:22–38:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:7\">PSA 33:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:13\">PSA 104:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:7\">PRO 2:7</a> <em>victory held in store for the righteous</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:13\">JER 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:16\">JER 51:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:5\">COL 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></p>\n<h2>Warnings against storing up selfishly or thoughtlessly</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:20\">JOB 20:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:24-Job31:28\">JOB 31:24–31:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:15–12:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:20-Luke19:23\">LUK 19:20–19:23</a></p>\n<h2>Storing up treasure in heaven</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:20\">MAT 6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33-Luke12:34\">LUK 12:33–12:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17-1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:17–6:19</a></p>\n<h2>Storing up sin and judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:12\">HOS 13:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's judgment is stored up</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:7\">2PE 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:22-Job38:23\">JOB 38:22–38:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:11\">ISA 26:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:17\">2PE 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:12-Jude1:13\">JUD 1:12–1:13</a></p>",
